Usage: reset_clock_latency [-help] <pin_or_clock_list> [-clock <clock_list>]
                           [-source]

-help                   # Prints out the command usage
<pin_or_clock_list>     # List of pins, ports or clock objects for which the
                        # assertions are removed (string, required)
-clock <clock_list>     # Removes latency associated with the clock list
                        # (string, optional)
-source                 # Removes source latency (bool, optional)